00:12:59,446 --> 00:13:01,240
You're acting
like it's your mother-in-law's arm,

234
00:13:01,323 --> 00:13:02,574
but what if it was your mom's arm?

235
00:13:02,658 --> 00:13:03,867
Come on, man.

236
00:13:04,993 --> 00:13:07,246
<i>No one's coming for that,
and Sonny wants it gone.</i>

237
00:13:07,829 --> 00:13:08,997
<i>It's not a big deal.</i>

238
00:13:30,018 --> 00:13:34,523
But, what if this wasn't an accident?
It doesn't feel right.

239
00:13:34,606 --> 00:13:37,860
I'm begging you for once,
do what's right for you.

240
00:13:37,943 --> 00:13:39,444
Ditch the fucking arm and come home.

241
00:13:46,785 --> 00:13:48,662
<i>Yancy knew that to get his job back</i>

242
00:13:48,745 --> 00:13:50,831
<i>all he had to do was stay out of trouble,</i>

243
00:13:51,331 --> 00:13:55,294
